@startuml
title Scrum 角色职责图

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "产品负责人\nProduct Owner" as po #lightgreen
actor "Scrum Master" as sm #lightyellow
component "开发团队\nDevelopment Team" as team #lightblue

package "产品负责人职责" {
    component [管理 Product Backlog] as po1
    component [确定优先级] as po2
    component [澄清需求] as po3
    component [接受或拒绝工作成果] as po4
    component [与利益相关者沟通] as po5
}

package "Scrum Master 职责" {
    component [促进 Scrum 流程] as sm1
    component [移除障碍] as sm2
    component [保护团队] as sm3
    component [指导团队] as sm4
    component [促进改进] as sm5
}

package "开发团队职责" {
    component [交付增量] as t1
    component [自我组织] as t2
    component [跨职能协作] as t3
    component [估算工作] as t4
    component [持续改进] as t5
}

' 角色到职责的关系
po --> po1
po --> po2
po --> po3
po --> po4
po --> po5

sm --> sm1
sm --> sm2
sm --> sm3
sm --> sm4
sm --> sm5

team --> t1
team --> t2
team --> t3
team --> t4
team --> t5

' 角色之间的关系
po <--> sm : 协作
sm <--> team : 服务和支持
po <--> team : 沟通需求

note right of po
  产品负责人是产品的单一决策者
  对产品的成功负责
  代表利益相关者的利益
end note

note right of sm
  Scrum Master 是团队的教练
  确保 Scrum 正确实施
  帮助团队遵循 Scrum 规则
end note

note right of team
  开发团队负责交付可工作的产品增量
  通常 3-9 人
  自组织、跨职能
end note

@enduml

